
**Example 1** (Create Get, Post, Put, Delete Request using **@Controller** and **@ResponseBody**)
Steps:

1. Create project using STS or Spring Initializr
1. Add Web Dependency in pom.xml
1. Create Domain Class (i.e. User)
1. Create UserController class
1. Add **@Controller** annotation to UserController class
1. Add **@RequestMapping** annotation to UserController class **@RequestMapping(value="api")**
1. Define static List users variable to simulate database and add 2 users to the list
1. Create new method to return all users in static list  (getAllUsers)
1. Add **@RequestMapping(value="users", method=RequestMethod.GET)** 
1. Run the application and call this URL **http://localhost:8080/api/users**
